        <tr bgcolor="#F7F7F7">
          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>Falcon2Z</b></font></td>
          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 08-15-99 04:11 AM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Could anyone tell me of the relative scarcity of regulars compared to the other currents? I've only been able to find one small display in one small store so far. Made me wonder if it was the higher price - $1.89 - for the package that caused fewer stores to stock them. Well, collectors, what has your success been in locating them?<br></font>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr bgcolor="#DEDFDF">
          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>Dustin Pezboy Tate</b></font></td>
          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 08-15-99 02:21 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I have never seen Regulars in stores. What stores carry them?<br></font>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr bgcolor="#F7F7F7">
          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>Canadian Lynx</b></font></td>
          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 08-15-99 04:17 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I have found a few at Albertsons, but that is the only place I have seen them. I think they are more expensive because they come with the peppermint pez. i dunno..</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr bgcolor="#DEDFDF">
          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>pezboy123456789</b></font></td>
          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 08-15-99 04:19 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I found some at a store called winn dixie. I think the reason they are more expensive is because they come with six packs of candy.</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr bgcolor="#F7F7F7">
          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>Insult 22</b></font></td>
          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 08-15-99 05:35 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I found a display of peppermint PEZ at Michael's about 5 months ago but they sold out of the dispensers very quickly. I only got a few of them before they were gone and they never got any more.</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr bgcolor="#DEDFDF">
          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>Pezmanmike</b></font></td>
          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 08-15-99 06:05 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Yeah, the regulars are very hard to find. But whats even more scarce are the Mono Regulars-these look just like the regulars except that (from what I heard) the inside sleeve is the same color as the dispenser.</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr bgcolor="#F7F7F7">
          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>Grimace076</b></font></td>
          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 08-15-99 06:11 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Are the mono regulars in a different package or something or are they just different inside? I have found the regulars at wal-mart before.</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr bgcolor="#DEDFDF">
          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>Pez Maniac</b></font></td>
          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 08-15-99 06:15 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">you can find regulars in Mars grocery stores here in glen burnie,md. hope that helps some.</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr bgcolor="#F7F7F7">
          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>pezta</b></font></td>
          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 08-17-99 07:33 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Mono regulars come in the exact same package as regular except that the inner sleeve which is usually white is the same colour as the outer stem... If you look at the dispenser from the bottom in the package u can tell. Monos are rare and there value is surprisingly high.</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
